户忠诚度**，从而增强平台对用户消费行为的留存能力。"], "parameters": {"model": "text-embedding-v4", "dimensions": 1024}}, "key": "embeddings_6cf31240a8bf4ff07abf50dc92894d66e6837f1435ca2be82273bc21f4bb2c33_v2"}